表的代码预览系统-配置表(OK)

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_config')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_config
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_config */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_config (
configID int not null,
discription nvarchar(30) null,
"values" nvarchar(200) null,
apptime datetime null,
constraint PK_SYS_CONFIG primary key (configID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('sys_config') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'系统-配置表(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_config')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'configID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'configID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'configID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'configID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_config')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'discription')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'discription'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'discription配置名称',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'discription'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_config')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'values')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'values'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'values配置值',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'values'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_config')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'apptime')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'apptime'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'apptime',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_config', 'column', 'apptime'
go
